project.name: TILDA - POI / POI Classification
project.description: TILDA processes points of interest and priority destinations for cycling network planning.

tags.description: Identify shopping destinations and retail points of interest for cycling network planning. All shop values are accepted.
POIs with access=private are excluded from processing. Only non-private POIs are included for cycling network planning.
